  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Efficacy of Different Strategies to Treat Anemia in Mexican Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Efficacy of Different Strategies to Treat Anemia in Mexican Children: A Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
